{"tid":340363,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"畫畫應該買ipad pro10.5定9.7","createTime":"2017-07-30T00:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T08:58:58.000Z","uid":36673,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2613e099afa42443e8f7c0f9c352dd03ece7817","tid":340363,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T00:37:07.000Z","msg":"唔做文書野，淨用procreate 畫畫、上網、睇Youtube，會隨身帶出街<br />\n<br />\n10.5就會買全新，但front back cover plus pencil 好似好甘下<br />\n<br />\n9.7就搵9成新2手or未開封機，而家好似唔算怪，連pencil應該都同10.5淨機差差唔多一千<br />\n<br />\n去store玩過10.5個mon的確好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但大部左重左（少少），spec又的確好好多，個人又有d完美主義唔會想有明顯有人用過既痕跡.....（例如smart keyboard完全唔明點接受買二手用）<br />\n<br />\n有無同樣畫畫為主既巴絲可以分享下<br />\n同埋由9.7upgrade上去既巴絲可以分享下理由，同有咩好正既地方<br />\n<br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea438cf15ac69508e070d301933ee6ec0afeee6c","tid":340363,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T00:41:44.000Z","msg":"你又前殼又後殼<br />\n淨機差果少少重量可以忽略啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1243a000bbcb807ee8707470fe05e92c63a56d36","tid":340363,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T00:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又前殼又後殼<br />\n淨機差果少少重量可以忽略啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但無計人垃圾成日跌到花晒，以前有部ipad3 硬殻都可以跌到爆"},{"pid":"51d6ee088ebb685e4c42954b3973ca60e68a547c","tid":340363,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T00:59:40.000Z","msg":"補充番少少<br />\n個人有一部mbp 13同Wacom companion 2<br />\n前者做文書design野後者就畫野-art station 咁，分開用無縛埋（部mac效能太廢），亦無位放external mon <br />\n<br />\n而家係差在一部portable 可以拎出街坐MTR/巴士畫野，同埋平時上網睇片睇reference 可以個mon大d （而家用緊5s...）<br />\n<br />\n以前有用ipad3+wacom第一代支19野+procreate畫野，但粒AAAA電玩完知後唔撚知邊到買到就無再咁做 （部ipad而家做左孝子）<br />\n<br />\nPro岩岩出個時都成日想買，但個期就買左部companion 同忙其他野；有諗過ipad9.7 甚至mini 加Wacom 新筆（1.9mm頭，係palm rejection on99）咁用，平好撚多，但始終信apple野多d，又一用可以用好多年下<br />\n<br />\n雖然都主要係銀包深度問題，10.5係買就起但係唔係真係但洗多千幾兩千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e14380951118e8b5d84715b445eb303e2fc1340","tid":340363,"uid":7966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T01:04:54.000Z","msg":"自己用落9.7經驗<br />\n9.7 有時寫字都見到少少少咁多delay, 相信畫畫更甚<br />\n10.5 應該會再啱畫畫多啲"},{"pid":"819541981350212d25f9466b5694f600e47f3fa7","tid":340363,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T01:31:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31217154545d28ea3adfdef4f9a89007a79f64c8","tid":340363,"uid":2893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:55:49.000Z","msg":"畫畫撚路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我由以前9.7開始用同畫，到後尾唔夠容量問題trade in咗部10.5<br />\n我覺得最多嘅分別係多咗ram, 彈app情況少咗<br />\n至於display 延遲方面，畫畫果陣我覺得個分別都幾難察覺<br />\n但平常用掃mon就明顯smooth 好多<br />\n同埋畫畫大mon啲都好啲<br />\n所以一定揀10.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f90bca44d12966dae4577349b9d43f2d96035b","tid":340363,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"畫畫撚路過<br />\n10.5吋，除左個mon 靚<br />\n架機的確快左，一般用途都好用好多<br />\n<br />\n利申有舊版12吋，個mon 好有時唔夠快"},{"pid":"1df3fe420043344fd1d00167b3cdd985935090e6","tid":340363,"uid":2893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補充番少少<br />\n個人有一部mbp 13同Wacom companion 2<br />\n前者做文書design野後者就畫野-art station 咁，分開用無縛埋（部mac效能太廢），亦無位放external mon <br />\n<br />\n而家係差在一部portable 可以拎出街坐MTR/巴士畫野，同埋平時上網睇片睇reference 可以個mon大d （而家用緊5s...）<br />\n<br />\n以前有用ipad3+wacom第一代支19野+procreate畫野，但粒AAAA電玩完知後唔撚知邊到買到就無再咁做 （部ipad而家做左孝子）<br />\n<br />\nPro岩岩出個時都成日想買，但個期就買左部companion 同忙其他野；有諗過ipad9.7 甚至mini 加Wacom 新筆（1.9mm頭，係palm rejection on99）咁用，平好撚多，但始終信apple野多d，又一用可以用好多年下<br />\n<br />\n雖然都主要係銀包深度問題，10.5係買就起但係唔係真係但洗多千幾兩千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n地鐵我唔敢拎部ipad出黎用，甚至畫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得人地𥄫住 好唔自在<br />\n<br />\n不過我都成日喺巴士畫<br />\n冇想像中咁爽，因為架車會chok下chok下<br />\n但快畫draft, sketch 真係一撚流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0d691056652b9ee9a4d0632a96c0fbf97ce796","tid":340363,"uid":106755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:09:51.000Z","msg":"畫畫不計重量的話，10.5當然比較好。<br />\n搭台請較一下各位：如果是用iPad air2 配Procreate 之類的app邊款筆好用，剛發現動漫節Wacom有折，或者有其他牌子推薦？ 謝謝大家先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/110923_6c147ed0cbc91b71318d00896b7ac10d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F110923_6c147ed0cbc91b71318d00896b7ac10d.jpg&h=c5859f1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc018187ee0712cce516d216c2b7c37317402087","tid":340363,"uid":96007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:48:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得pro畫野好滑都唔好畫"},{"pid":"b1370a497de1a55bdc9816fba4b49e0b2f46d2a8","tid":340363,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"唔該晒咁多位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎荷包夠深真係10.5會比較好"},{"pid":"7c8cdba96eb86be2c8ea1d67b22fd79695265c2f","tid":340363,"uid":1327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:12:49.000Z","msg":"12.9 最好"},{"pid":"c778e2cff42555bd535baff1e60e393af3a4e6cd","tid":340363,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畫畫不計重量的話，10.5當然比較好。<br />\n搭台請較一下各位：如果是用iPad air2 配Procreate 之類的app邊款筆好用，剛發現動漫節Wacom有折，或者有其他牌子推薦？ 謝謝大家先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/110923_6c147ed0cbc91b71318d00896b7ac10d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F110923_6c147ed0cbc91b71318d00896b7ac10d.jpg&h=c5859f1f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣我答到XD<br />\nWacom / adonit <br />\n但都係前者比較好同係香港容易d買到~ <br />\n筆有好多支，要睇你用咩機同software，每一支都略有不同, 但palm protection 通常都麻麻，要吊手/舖手巾/帶手套畫<br />\n<br />\n最新個支係Wacom sketch<br />\n上一代係fineline3，再對上有fineline/ creative stylus <br />\nAir2既話應該fineline3就ok, 我check過同sketch分別主要在於後者有個好靚既portable case同支援iPad pro series <br />\n<br />\n建議你上官網check多次<br />\nYoutube有大量artistic Review<br />\n識/唔怕睇日文可以睇有個網叫iPad creator ，入面有極大量各種app同筆既情報同review，包括上面提過既所有野及unboxing"},{"pid":"3ada6a59bafe3b8459a6a7c49b9361fad15d0c27","tid":340363,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12.9 最好</blockquote><br />\n難d帶出街麻，已經係成部laptop個大小...<br />\n巴打你係機主加畫畫？"},{"pid":"5a18148577b62f8f9ca85bd91aea62b5e60cc58e","tid":340363,"uid":132055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你又前殼又後殼<br />\n淨機差果少少重量可以忽略啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但無計人垃圾成日跌到花晒，以前有部ipad3 硬殻都可以跌到爆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有新買新 2GB Ram 同4GB Ram既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 iPad Air2用到爆mon四角變形部機<strong> 攣埋</strong>"},{"pid":"8343d74dc928ae69bfb107521151e5c2a88a86f4","tid":340363,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人覺得pro畫野好滑都唔好畫</blockquote><br />\n覺, 尤其一有指紋真係唔好畫<br />\n貼磨沙貼之後好畫好多"},{"pid":"0be904ad200b329490fa13c6b6b3185753c471be","tid":340363,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人覺得pro畫野好滑都唔好畫</blockquote><br />\n覺, 尤其一有指紋真係唔好畫<br />\n貼磨沙貼之後好畫好多</blockquote><br />\n想問下磨沙貼用起黎係點，唔反光？會唔會好影響個mon色水？用筆會唔會好刮？（刮筆尖/塊貼？）<br />\n追d post 好多都話用筆裸mon用最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27df95f1f9cd8b40762f59eab50c1d97ea82072","tid":340363,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你又前殼又後殼<br />\n淨機差果少少重量可以忽略啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但無計人垃圾成日跌到花晒，以前有部ipad3 硬殻都可以跌到爆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有新買新 2GB Ram 同4GB Ram既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 iPad Air2用到爆mon四角變形部機<strong> 攣埋</strong></blockquote><br />\n好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599885205fa532e0ab143717a39d2976e5372851","tid":340363,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"唔畫畫係咪都係買返9.7算？"},{"pid":"a8c9855dea3182dc97cb1ec9bfacda27d457aacf","tid":340363,"uid":132055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你又前殼又後殼<br />\n淨機差果少少重量可以忽略啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但無計人垃圾成日跌到花晒，以前有部ipad3 硬殻都可以跌到爆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有新買新 2GB Ram 同4GB Ram既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 iPad Air2用到爆mon四角變形部機<strong> 攣埋</strong></blockquote><br />\n好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有圖有真相今晚影俾你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42f774dc2b9faa1f11c0d58b66a278098dd1bcc","tid":340363,"uid":1972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:14:48.000Z","msg":"9.7=trash"},{"pid":"c49b04658ddcd9f02096ddc6cd9510ae1cb3834b","tid":340363,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人覺得pro畫野好滑都唔好畫</blockquote><br />\n覺, 尤其一有指紋真係唔好畫<br />\n貼磨沙貼之後好畫好多</blockquote><br />\n想問下磨沙貼用起黎係點，唔反光？會唔會好影響個mon色水？用筆會唔會好刮？（刮筆尖/塊貼？）<br />\n追d post 好多都話用筆裸mon用最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知其他人點畫, 但係我一開始用祼筆祼mon 感覺好怪<br />\n因為覺得好跣同feel到指毛有阻力, 成日抹mon又煩<br />\n所以貼磨沙貼保護個mon, 手感似返cintiq 個mon好多<br />\n支筆其實幾尖, 張貼而家都花花地<br />\n個mon 色差視乎mon貼質素, 但覺得分別唔大<br />\n<br />\n利申 電腦畫既話會用Wacom cintiq 13&quot;"},{"pid":"35c3824e89a8563e4226e46f50a25762cfe3a1f3","tid":340363,"uid":132055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你又前殼又後殼<br />\n淨機差果少少重量可以忽略啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但無計人垃圾成日跌到花晒，以前有部ipad3 硬殻都可以跌到爆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有新買新 2GB Ram 同4GB Ram既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 iPad Air2用到爆mon四角變形部機<strong> 攣埋</strong></blockquote><br />\n好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連個lock制都㩒唔到<br />\nMic又壞<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/093032_aa7a1f8877d0008c504cf8fb6c4ea0a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F093032_aa7a1f8877d0008c504cf8fb6c4ea0a9.jpg&h=2fd50582&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/093034_4ae9773a8691fcc8ca041ab3ea1b3fe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F093034_4ae9773a8691fcc8ca041ab3ea1b3fe3.jpg&h=5be610c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/093038_9528040f59afd05c148ee7387afe93ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F093038_9528040f59afd05c148ee7387afe93ca.jpg&h=768bf1c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5642b7591cc618500dbac0feddb531460682a4e6","tid":340363,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"10.5起碼無咁快out, ipad 得2gb,我諗ios11都係極限了。<br />\n<br />\n個芒真係完全兩個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}